effects.display_string:
Set: Your abilities have a chance to start a Winning Streak! increasing the damage of Rampage by 2%, stacking up to 10 times.
Rampage has a 15% chance to end your Winning Streak!

Set: When you gain a stack of Winning Streak! you have an even chance to either cause your next Bloodthirst to deal 15% increased damage and have 25% increased chance to critically strike or cause your next Raging Blow to deal 15% increased damage and generate 2 additional Rage.

spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 3 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 144,300  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Use: Unleash your inner tempest to gain 9,927 Strength for 15 sec. Your next 3 abilities cause a lightning blast dealing 550,022 Nature damage to your primary target. Damage increased by 100% with each subsequent blast. (2 Min Cooldown)
